## Output Format

```
## EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
One paragraph describing the cognitive experience of using this interface — what a typical user's brain goes through, what works, what causes friction.

**Cognitive Experience Score: X/10**

---

## CRITICAL FRICTION POINTS 🔴
[High-effort or high-confusion moments — likely causing drop-off]

## FRICTION TO REDUCE 🟡
[Suboptimal cognitive experiences — worth improving]

## OPPORTUNITIES 🟢
[Places where better psychology could significantly improve outcomes]

## PSYCHOLOGICAL STRENGTHS ✅
[What the product does well cognitively — learn from these]

